				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "One of four messenger rats being trained in Jaheira's basement. One of four messenger rats being trained in Jaheira's basement. The rats themselves are relatively new, excitable, and often get the details of their intel wrong. Each hints at a different event around the city, getting it just a little bit off."
